OL,3,CGrooming gang leader moved after
OL,4,Chostel address revealed on social media
OL,6,FRochdale grooming gang leader Shabir
OL,7,FAhmed has been moved from his
OL,8,Faccommodation after its location was
OL,9,Frevealed on social media.
OL,11,FPakistani-born Ahmed, 73, known to his
OL,12,Fvictims as "Daddy", was released on
OL,13,Flicence on 2 July after he served 14
OL,14,Fyears in jail since his conviction in
OL,15,F2012 for multiple rape and sexual
OL,16,Foffences against young girls.
OL,26,@tD@LOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
