PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784274472
OL,3,CGrooming gang leader moved after
OL,4,Chostel address revealed on social media
OL,6,FHe is subject to a string of licence
OL,7,Fconditions including staying at
OL,8,Fapproved accommodation staffed 24
OL,9,Fhours a day, but the disclosure of the
OL,10,Faddress in Accrington, Lancashire,
OL,11,Fcaused local uproar.
OL,13,FAmong those who called for his removal
OL,14,Ffrom the town were Sarah Smith, Labour
OL,15,FMP for Hyndburn and Haslingden.
OL,17,FIn a statement, she said: "Since
OL,18,Ffinding out that Shabir Ahmed had been
OL,19,Freleased from prison into Hyndburn, I
OL,20,Fdid everything in my power to get him
OL,21,Fremoved.
OL,26,@yD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784274472
OL,3,CGrooming gang leader moved after
OL,4,Chostel address revealed on social media
OL,6,F"I can confirm that he has been moved.
OL,7,FMy thanks go to the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice, the Home Office, and
OL,9,FLancashire Police for ensuring this
OL,10,Foutcome.
OL,12,F"I am disgusted that he was ever here
OL,13,Fin the first place and I join other MP
OL,14,Fcolleagues who have been calling for a
OL,15,Fmuch wider exclusion zone so that he
OL,16,Fis not placed in Lancashire or the
OL,17,FNorth West.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784274472
OL,3,CGrooming gang leader moved after
OL,4,Chostel address revealed on social media
OL,6,F"He must be deported as soon as
OL,7,Fpossible, and I am pleased the
OL,8,FGovernment is taking steps to secure
OL,9,Fthis.
OL,11,F"My first thoughts are with his
OL,12,Fvictims. His release will bring back
OL,13,Funimaginable trauma for the women
OL,14,Fwhose lives were changed forever by
OL,15,Fhis sickening crimes. They deserved to
OL,16,Fknow that once he left prison, he
OL,17,Fwould leave this country.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784274472
OL,3,CGrooming gang leader moved after
OL,4,Chostel address revealed on social media
OL,6,F"Instead, they have been told he
OL,7,Fremains here, far too close to the
OL,8,Fscenes of his crimes and to his
OL,9,Fvictims."
OL,11,FA Ministry of Justice spokeswoman
OL,12,Fsaid: "Public protection is our top
OL,13,Fpriority. This offender is subject to
OL,14,Fthe toughest supervision possible and
OL,15,Fhe will be on the sex offenders
OL,16,Fregister for life.
OL,18,F"He is also banned from contacting his
OL,19,Fvictims, or any child or young person,
OL,20,Fand has his movements tracked."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]tD@GOUzD@AOU|D@_O]
