CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784274472
OL,3,CGrooming gang leader moved after
OL,4,Chostel address revealed on social media
OL,6,FAhmed cannot return to his former home
OL,7,Faddress in Oldham and is also excluded
OL,8,Ffrom parts of Rochdale.
OL,10,FOn Monday, Home Secretary Shabana
OL,11,FMahmood said she would change the
OL,12,FImmigration and Asylum Bill, which is
OL,13,Fpassing through the Commons, to remove
OL,14,Fimmunity under the 1971 Immigration
OL,15,FAct which would prevent Ahmed being
OL,16,Fdeported.
OL,18,FHowever she admitted in the Commons
OL,19,Fthat despite the potential law change,
OL,20,Fshe would be unable to deport him
OL,21,Funless Pakistan agrees to do so.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
